Steampunk Calculators
---------------------

A game by Eduardo Gonzalez and Josh Albrecht.

Music is "3 Ghosts I" from Nine Inch Nails, and is under a creative commons
license: (CC:BY-NC-SA)

To play:
--------

Download python (version 2.5 recommended) and pygame.

Then, run the steamcalc.py script.

Objective:
----------

To get to the goal (the infinity circle) by jumping around, using
steam vents, and avoiding vicious dot eating calculators!

For an extra challenge, pick up the (g) circle at the beginning of a
level to disable your firepower!

Controls:
---------

Left / A - move left
Right / D - move right
Up / W - jumps

Left click - shoot
Right click - build